---
title: Linguine, Chicken and Bacon in Blush Sauce with Baby Tomatoes, Corn and Crispy Shallots
description: The swirl of rosy colour in this luscious, blushing linguine dish comes from sweet baby tomatoes. The sauce is boosted even more with chicken, bacon, corn and a sprinkle of crispy shallots. You'll be licking the plate clean!
